chunks.content:
=== 文档：Report Guidelines.pdf ===

University of Macau 
Department of Computer and Information Science

Report Guidelines

1. Introduction
Every internship report should include at least 10 pages of content covering your experience, learnings, and reflections.

2. Report Structure
The internship report should include:
- Executive Summary (1 page)
- Introduction (1-2 pages)  
- Work Experience Description (3-4 pages)
- Technical Skills Acquired (2-3 pages)
- Challenges and Solutions (1-2 pages)
- Conclusion and Reflection (1 page)
